# multiple iterations have taken place, this is the current recipe

# ingredients
100g rye
200g whole meal
800g bakers white
200g starter
850g water
23g salt

makes 2 loaf.

# process
mix together
20 mins fold
1 hour fold
repeat 3 times, 1 hour apart
let bulk till 50% increase
split, rest 15 mins
shape
cold proof 18 hours
score 

dutch oven pre heat to 250c
in, lid on, bake 20 mins 
lid off, drop temp to 230c, bake 35 mins
rest at least 2 hours
